* SPICE model rectifier diode 1N4007 (Fixed for KiCad/Ngspice)
* Based on Diotec Semiconductor AG model
* ---------------------------------------------------------
.subckt 1N4007 A K params: Vrrm=1000 Vrsm=1000 Ir=5u Irsm=5u Vf=1.1 Ifav=1 Rs=.05 trr=1500n Cj=15p Eg=1.11 Xti=3

* Definition of the Diode Model
* Removed LTspice specific params: Vpk, Iave, Vp, mfg, type
.model Rectifier D(
+ Is={Ir/40}
+ Bv={Vrsm*1.05}
+ Ibv={Ir}
+ N={.8*Vf/25m/(ln(Ifav)-ln(Ir/40))}
+ Rs={Rs}
+ Eg={Eg}
+ Xti={Xti}
+ Cjo={Cj*2}
+ M=.33
+ Tt={trr}
+ )

* Connecting the Diode
D A K Rectifier

.ends
